  "headline": "Analog Devices (ADI) Intrinsic Value: A DCF Analysis",
  "description": "A transparent, step-by-step discounted cash flow valuation of Analog Devices, Inc. Using actual FY2025 financials to arrive at a single fair value estimate for ADI shares.",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-18",
  "dateModified": "2026-03-18",
